**************************
** Multipass Cheatsheet **
**************************

Launch an instance using default current Ubuntu LTS
$ multipass launch --name ubuntu-lts

Run commands in that instance and exit when done
$ multipass exec <name> -- lsb_release -a

Enter shell of the instance
$ multipass shell <name>

List instances
$ multipass list

Stop and start instances
$ multipass start <name> <another-name>
$ multipass stop <name>

Delete and purge instances
$ multipass delete <name>
$ multipass purge

Get instance information
$ multipass info <name>

Find alternate images to launch with Multipass (apart from default LTS)
$ multipass find

Get help
$ multipass help

Reference
https://multipass.run
